      "text": "Deewu: Tu eſſi manniam Teh- wam Dahwidam leelu Schehta- ſtibu parahdijs/ un eſſi mann par Kehnixu darrijs winna Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad KUNGGS Deews! lai taws Wahrdz teefcham ta noteek/ fo tu us mannu Tehwu Dahwidu runnajs eſſi/ jo tu eſſi manni par Kehnixu darrijs/ pahr Landim/ kas tik dauds irr/ ka Pihschli us Semnes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad dohd nu man Gud- ribu un Sapraschannu/ ka escho Lauschu Preezſcha iſceemu un ee- eemu/ jo kas warretu tahdu lee- lu Lauschu Pulku teefacht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Deewe us Salamannu: Tapehz ka tas irr tawa Sirđi bijis/ un tu ne eſſi praftijs Baggattbu/ nedś Man- tas/ nedś Bohdu/ nedś tawn Ee- naidneeku Dwehțeleś/ nedś ilgu Dshwoſchanu/ bet tueſſi tewim Gudribu un Sapraschann lub- dsis/ ka tu mannuś Landis tee- faht warri/ pahr fo es tew eſmu par Kehnixu eezeblig.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad taps tew Gudriba un Sapraschana dohta/ ir Bag- gatibu un Mantas/ un Bohdu es tew arridsan dobschu/ kahds ne weenam Kehnixam bijis/ kas preeſſch tew bijuschi/ un pehz tew arridsan tahds ne buhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta nahze Salamans us Jeruſaleimi no ta Augstuma/kas Gibeonā bija no tahs Sa-eescha- nas Telts/ un wiꞥſch walōja pahr Iſraelu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Salamans tapulzeja Rattus un Zahntneekus/ un wiꞥſch nam bij tuhktoschf un tschetr- ſints Ratti/ un dwipadefinits tuhktoschi Zahntneeki/ un wiꞥſch likke tohs Rattu-Pilskahṭōs un pee ta Kehnixa Jeruſaleime.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Kehnisch darri- ja/ ka tik dands Sudraba un Selta Jeruſaleme bija/ ka Akint- xi/ un to Zeedra-Kohlu darrija wiꞥſch tik dauds/ ka Mescha Wihges-Kohki Eelelijās irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Salamanam tappe Sirgi no Egiptes atwesti/ un wiﬀada Prezze / un ta Kehnina Prezzineeki pirzin pirke to paschu Prezzi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ratti tappe no Egip- tes augſcham atwesti par fesch- ſunts Sudraba Gabbaleem/ un weens Sirgs par ſints un peez- defmits. Ta iswedde tee tohs zaurwinnu Kohku preekſch wiſf- fein Kehnineem to Getiteru/ un to Sihreru Kehnineem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta II. Nodalla.\nSalamans eeſelt Strahdneekus un Uṣragus pahr teem : 1. Praża no Fraimu to Nehuis an no Tirns Kohkus/ ka to Deewa Nam- mu warri uſtaisht : 3. Un weenn ſaprat- tigu Ammatneeku : 7. Ko wiꞥſch arri wiſu dabbu : 11. To Strahdneeku Pulks : 17.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N Salamans dohmaja preeſſch ta KUNGGA Wahrdz weenu Nam- mu darriht/ un weenu Nammu preeſſch tawn Wahſtibu.\n"
